# Cloudflare Pages redirects.
#
# /dl/* — single source of truth is the latest GitHub Release on
# shinyobjectz-sh/workbooks. The release pipeline at
# packages/workbooksd/release/release.sh creates the release; this file
# just points downloads at it. Everything in /dl/ is a redirect, no
# binaries are stored here or in git.
#
# Format: <source-path>  <destination-url>  <status-code>
# :splat captures the wildcard.

/dl/*  https://github.com/shinyobjectz-sh/workbooks/releases/latest/download/:splat  302
